  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Update Typography System on About Us Page\n\nImprove the typography and text formatting on the About Us page to create a visually appealing, readable, and well-structured layout.\n\nRequirements:\n- Fix heading hierarchy and styling to establish clear visual structure\n- Apply consistent, readable font sizes and line heights throughout\n- Reformat list elements with proper spacing and visual indicators\n- Ensure adequate contrast between text and background colors\n- Set appropriate paragraph spacing and max-width for optimal reading line length\n- Apply consistent styling for different text elements (body text, quotes, captions)\n- Verify typography looks good across different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Consider using web-safe or properly loaded custom fonts with appropriate fallbacks\n\nSuccess criteria:\n- Headings follow a logical visual hierarchy (H1 > H2 > H3)\n- Lists are well-spaced with clear visual structure\n- Text is comfortably readable without strain\n- Overall page has a polished, professional appearance",
